txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Gauredain and goblins in the eastern reaches of the Misty Mountains. You can deliver these items to Afwald within the ruins at Hrimbarg in the Misty Mountains.
'Good to know that their number is dwindling every time that you step out into the wild, thank you.'

'The goblins and Gauredain in this area are vile creatures. They attacked us and forced us to this place. Now vengeance is not always the best option, but thinning their number out is a necessity if we are to ever leave. Bring me their sword sheaths and broken weapons.'
Thorin's Hall Task: Gilded Sword Sheaths
Afwald, the provisioner at the dwarf-ruin of Hrimbarg, awaits the return of gilded sword sheaths.
Deliver the gilded sword sheaths to Afwald within the ruins of Hrimbarg in the Misty Mountains

You have accepted a task to deliver gilded sword sheaths from the Gauredain and goblins found in the eastern reaches of the Misty Mountains to Afwald. Afwald can be found within the ruins at Hrimbarg, also found in the Misty Mountains.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Gauredain and goblins in the eastern reaches of the Misty Mountains.
